# Cloudflare Pages — Response Headers
# Configures correct MIME types and security for MHTML assets

# Serve MHTML files as multipart/related so browsers render them inline
/*.mhtml
  Content-Type: multipart/related; type="text/html"; charset=UTF-8
  X-Frame-Options: SAMEORIGIN
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff

# Security headers for all pages
/*
  X-Frame-Options: SAMEORIGIN
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
  Referrer-Policy: strict-origin-when-cross-origin
